reviewText: If you are planning a trip to Northern Ethiopia of just interested this is a great video and the host provides lots of good information.
i never asked for it i love to have it but i don't have it august

The "ancient history" coverage is less than half of this DVD; the majority is of today's cities, the produce, tourist accommodations & population of Northern Ethiopia. There is too much duplication of "Ethiopia - Worlds Together". I would appreciate Amazon being more specific about similarities in the "educational & historical coverage" of their DVDs.
